metadata.name: Dancing flowers under sunshine
metadata.description: As the sun slowly descends below the horizon, its warm golden rays illuminate the sky with a breathtaking display of colors. The petals of flowers seem to glow in the fading light, as if they are basking in the last rays of sunshine before nightfall. Amongst them stands a lone lavender flower, its delicate petals gently swaying in the gentle breeze. The scene is so serene and peaceful that it fills your heart with a sense of tranquility and calmness. It's as if time has stood still for a moment, allowing you to soak in the beauty of nature and feel its healing power was over you.
